  "body": "**Preconditions:** User A and User B are mutual contacts. \r\n\r\n**Steps:** \r\n\r\n1. Create Require approval community by User A\r\n2. Share community link to User B\r\n3. Open community link by User B\r\n4. Send access request to community by User B\r\n5. Check if unread badge on AC icon appeared for User B after sending a request\r\n\r\n**Actual result:** Unread badge appears on AC icon after sending community access request. There are no unread notifications in AC. Unread badge remains to be shown and does not disappear in future. \r\n\r\n**Expected result:**  unread indicator should not appear for user after sending community access request, as currently we don't send any notifications to sender. \r\n\r\n[sender_of_comm_request.zip](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/files/10490574/sender_of_comm_request.zip)\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/97245802/214312291-4d485e39-9c67-48e7-b20f-f5538cce0e8e.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
